<p>Tom arrived in the Sunshine State on September 8 by private jet.</p>

<p>He is starring in Baz Luhrmann's Elvis Presley biopic, in which he is playing the rock legend's manager Colonel Tom Parker. </p>

<p>The star and his wife Rita Wilson tested positive for COVID-19 during another visit to Australia in March.</p>

